T1  - OUTPATIENT ANALYTIC ASSESSMENT OF ANOREXIA NERVOSA - THE IMPORTANCE OF VENOUS BLOOD GASES.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1590/1984-0462/2020/38/2018358
A1  - Pires, Sofia Alexandra Pereira
A1  - Soares, Joana Costa
